questions.quote: Jerry, have you ever seen the movie The Other Side Of Darkness?
Yeah, on one hand he's smart with rockets and on the other hand he's dumb with parking. . . . It's cold out here huh?
Well, nothing. It's no skin off my hide if people like to look. I just didn't see what the big attraction was.
Oh, actually, I really prefer to sit here. I don't hear very well out of this ear  so, I always try to sit to the right of people.
We've been trying to get it out of him for ten years. What is it?
Jerry! I need you to get another picture of man-hands. I'm beggin' you!
I don't know, what were you doing opening her medicine cabinet?
You know, I couldn't bring myself to spend one of these. I got some kind of a-a-a-a-a phobia.
Hey, you know you gotta get permission from me. I'm the super. Who said you could do that?
I will - don't worry.  In fact, I'll have her bring up a whole case of the stuff. It'll be really heavy. Let's see if she likes sitting on a plane with a big box on her lap!
